Welcome to Choosing UC Riverside!Thank you for visiting our site. Each week we feature a profile on one of the students who has chosen to attend UC Riverside as a way of helping you get to know some of the nearly 17,000 students who are currently part of our campus community.The students featured on this site have been selected from a wide cross section of our campus. They have volunteered to share some of their thoughts about their decision to attend UC Riverside, what excites them about being here and their plans for the future.Check back often to meet more of our students. You will also be able to browse the archive if you happen to miss a student featured at a particular time.